OL,3,CFour in court over arson attack on
OL,4,CJewish community ambulances
OL,6,FThree men and a youth have appeared at
OL,7,Fthe Old Bailey accused of destroying
OL,8,Ffour Jewish community ambulances in an
OL,9,Farson attack.
OL,11,FIn the early hours of March 23, three
OL,12,Fpeople allegedly set fire to the fully
OL,13,Fstocked vehicles in north London,
OL,14,Fwhile a fourth waited in a blue Toyota
OL,15,FAvensis.
OL,17,FThe resulting blaze caused gas
OL,18,Fcanisters inside the ambulances to
OL,19,Fexplode, resulting in around #1
OL,20,Fmillion of damage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
