OL,3,CFour in court over arson attack on
OL,4,CJewish community ambulances
OL,6,FNearby flats and a synagogue were also
OL,7,Fdamaged by the fire, the court heard.
OL,9,FThe ambulances belonged to Hatzola, a
OL,10,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,11,Foperating in the Golders Green area of
OL,12,Fnorth London.
OL,14,FProsecutors have said they believe the
OL,15,Fincident was a targeted attack against
OL,16,Fthe Jewish community.
OL,18,FOn Friday, Hamza Iqbal, 20, Rehan
OL,19,FKhan, 19, Judex Atshatshi, 18, and a
OL,20,F17-year-old boy, appeared at the Old
OL,21,FBailey charged with criminal damage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
