FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777198006
OL,3,CFour in court over arson attack on
OL,4,CJewish community ambulances
OL,6,FThe details of the charge state that
OL,7,F"without lawful excuse" they destroyed
OL,8,Ffour ambulances valued at over #5,000
OL,9,Fbelonging to the Hatzola charity.
OL,11,FIt is alleged that the defendants
OL,12,Fintended to destroy or damage the
OL,13,Fproperty or were "reckless" as to
OL,14,Fwhether it would be destroyed and life
OL,15,Fendangered.
OL,17,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb set a plea
OL,18,Fhearing on August 28 and a provisional
OL,19,Ffour-week trial at the Old Bailey from
OL,20,FJanuary 27 next year.
