OL,3,CFour in court over arson attack on
OL,4,CJewish community ambulances
OL,6,FIqbal and Khan, from Leyton, east
OL,7,FLondon, Atshatshi, from Dagenham, east
OL,8,FLondon, and the 17-year-old boy, of
OL,9,Fdual British-Pakistani nationality,
OL,10,Ffrom Walthamstow, were remanded into
OL,11,Fcustody.
